    <guid isPermaLink="false">http://quotesfromtheunderground.wordpress.com/?p=1190</guid>
    <description/>
    <content:encoded><![CDATA[Q. Can one encourage the intellectual centre to work? 

  A. Cultivate attention. You will see that then it gives different results. Think with attention. Do not let yourself think mechanically. Mechanical thinking transforms itself into imagination.]]></content:encoded>
